15:01.066 --> 15:02.066 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
What went wrong?

15:02.066 --> 15:04.133 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

15:04.133 --> 15:06.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BERNIE SANDERS (I), Vermont:
Well, what went wrong, Judy, is
they brought forth a disastrous

15:06.200 --> 15:10.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
