Medical Association,
the American Hospital
Association, the AARP.

15:19.866 --> 15:24.000 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And virtually every national
health care organization
understood that, when
you throw 22 million

15:27.700 --> 15:32.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
