conditions to get the health
care they need and can afford,

15:43.966 --> 15:45.633 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
you know what?

15:45.633 --> 15:46.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
You have got a bill
that's a stinker, it
shouldn't go anyplace.

15:46.966 --> 15:48.500 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And it didn't go anyplace.

15:48.500 --> 15:50.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And that's a good thing
for the American people.

15:50.900 --> 15:55.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And I thank the millions
of people who stood up
and fought back and said
that that legislation

15:57.066 --> 15:59.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
is not what this
country is about.

15:59.166 --> 16:02.166 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
