work with Republicans?

16:49.066 --> 16:50.066 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

16:50.066 --> 16:52.200 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
BERNIE SANDERS: Of course.

16:52.200 --> 16:55.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
