pharmaceutical industry.

17:14.066 --> 17:18.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, if the Republicans want
to sit town and say how do we
improve the Affordable Care

17:20.066 --> 17:23.200 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Act, not destroy it, how
