go forward and do that.

17:23.200 --> 17:25.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I have some very
specific ideas on that.

17:25.333 --> 17:28.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Well,
