you and others, are.

17:32.166 --> 17:33.866 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Where's the middle ground here?

17:33.866 --> 17:35.366 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Where do you see a
place for compromise?

17:35.366 --> 17:36.566 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

17:36.566 --> 17:38.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
BERNIE SANDERS:
Well, I'll tell you.

17:38.633 --> 17:41.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
As I just mentioned, the cost
of prescription drugs in this
country is far, far higher than

17:41.700 --> 17:43.733 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
