industry and it was going to
lower prescription drug costs.

17:52.200 --> 17:54.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Well, we have some
ideas to do that.

17:54.166 --> 17:56.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Republicans may
have other ideas.

17:56.666 --> 18:00.633 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Let's talk about lowering
prescription drug costs,
saving the federal
government substantial

18:00.633 --> 18:02.633 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
