are offering or there is no
offer, let them have at least

18:26.266 --> 18:28.300 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
a public option.

18:28.300 --> 18:32.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Number three, I believe that
the American people would
very much like to see lowering

18:33.800 --> 18:38.466 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
