to all people as a right.

18:51.366 --> 18:54.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And that is why I will be
introducing a Medicare-for-all
single-payer programs.

18:54.933 --> 18:58.066 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It will not be passed, believe
