over two weeks.

49:38.166 --> 49:42.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Party told the "NewsHour" he
was inspired by the notion
that, no matter what happens,

49:42.466 --> 49:45.200 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
