in the morning.

49:45.200 --> 49:50.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
NICOLAS PARTY, Artist: I was
aware of the circle shape of the
building, and that influenced

49:50.800 --> 49:52.866 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
my decision.

49:52.866 --> 49:56.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
