when I work on the walls.

50:37.900 --> 50:41.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
So I use the wall almost
as a piece of paper.

50:41.633 --> 50:46.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Sometimes, of course, I have
sketches, but, yes, I work
very organically, so there's an

50:46.500 --> 50:47.866 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
