painting sunsets and sunrises.

51:05.766 --> 51:10.500 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's the only moment
during the day that you
can really see, visually,
how the entire universe

51:12.033 --> 51:13.433 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
