of Earth at that moment.

51:15.300 --> 51:17.400 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Right now, we can't see it.

51:17.400 --> 51:20.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But during those 30 minutes
of a sunset or a sunrise, you
can actually feel it, and you

51:20.833 --> 51:22.866 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
