51:22.866 --> 51:27.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And all those kind of different
reasons that the color change
the sky, that's the physical

51:29.766 --> 51:31.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
reaction of the light
going through different
kind of angles and stuff.

51:31.833 --> 51:34.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And I thought
that's fascinating.

51:34.300 --> 51:39.200 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Obviously, the daily life
and our little preoccupations
that are very important,
but so it's interesting

51:40.566 --> 51:42.766 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
