that is very slow and
allow myself a lot of time.

51:49.500 --> 51:52.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Then there's a moment when it's
-- everything is beginning to
build up, and I realize, oh,

51:52.733 --> 51:56.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
